title: Forest_Prediction_Final
description: In this competition you are asked to predict the forest cover type (the predominant kind of tree cover) from strictly cartographic variables (as opposed to remotely sensed data). The data is in raw form (not scaled) and contains binary columns of data for qualitative independent variables such as wilderness areas and soil type.
